{"tid":1396073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論] 往後的星期六 ,日遊行示威的策略","createTime":"2019-08-02T03:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T04:32:24.000Z","uid":94771,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1923a9772c030f71c90b9716d194ddb52634b2","tid":1396073,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:25:17.000Z","msg":"希望大家認真討論 唔好太比主觀感覺影響到自己 <br />\n好老實我好迷網 唔知點先對個運動最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續依家條勇武路線 每次都活動完後守路 :<br />\n好處:<br />\n1. 可以再比壓力警犬<br />\n2. 增加犬犯錯機會<br />\n3. 令政府感到壓力<br />\n4. 象徵意義<br />\n5. 運動不同意義上的保溫 不論好壞<br />\n<br />\n壞處:<br />\n1. 勇武手足被捕 而且全部會被司法迫害<br />\n2. 勇武手足受傷 警犬更強的武力<br />\n3. 令淺黃,中立對衝突畫面厭倦 變到 不參與及後活動 (變成花生派)<br />\n4. 佔多數的和理非示威人數因害怕衝突及控罪減少<br />\n5. 運動續戰力較差 比較難把運動拉長 因為愈來愈多人被捕 同 和理非變花生派<br />\n<br />\n暫時轉做和理非 遊完慢慢散水 :<br />\n好處:<br />\n1. 令多數的和理非示威人數可以增加返 運動可以回氣<br />\n2. 令中立派轉向更加針對政府<br />\n3. 運動的續戰力可以拉長<br />\n4. 依邊的手足唔會犯錯 輿論戰取場得優勢(輿論戰上)<br />\n<br />\n壞處:<br />\n1. 對政府的施壓力較細<br />\n2. 警犬壓力比較上無咁大<br />\n3. 有保溫能力，但畫面無咁震撼<br />\n<br />\n個人意見<br />\n依個星期可以轉返做和理非表態同通碟 之後政府唔理就返去勇武路線。<br />\n一星期和理非 一星期勇武 不斷做通碟<br />\n盡量將戰線持續到10月1 搞高人數大遊行 落9共慘黨70周年面"},{"pid":"f041ad5a0eece6c37435793938008a12d3d0f550","tid":1396073,"uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/iz0C2NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz0C2NO.jpg&h=82e26671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZEfzkzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEfzkzy.jpg&h=8043d3d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea51d9b4e3a514226efb26418e6ee9438ef3f9c4","tid":1396073,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/OosJYdV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOosJYdV.png&h=026dcef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2862b5213b9437ab48f1514100420b611a9a5f6","tid":1396073,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072481e39477db2ae76bc844fbdaa3f9f0b40688","tid":1396073,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"圍警署 等防暴 散<br />\n無目的 打遊擊"},{"pid":"dbe407be29d55f39eee3723b2632d8e330ec70db","tid":1396073,"uid":182998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"141d1df4ac98e1a05bfa3be0dd0c76d366553710","tid":1396073,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f041ad5a0eece6c37435793938008a12d3d0f550","tid":1396073,"uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/iz0C2NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiz0C2NO.jpg&h=82e26671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZEfzkzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEfzkzy.jpg&h=8043d3d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:37:28.000Z","msg":"呢2張圖超正"},{"pid":"9cad8953dac427f9376c0ff39664afbaa5f1fe65","tid":1396073,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a7bd36623946f097991e0a689a4122f947142d","tid":1396073,"uid":268824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"推推 仲有兩個月要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"